history.content: I'm in a similar position as @13765 where I completed all of my graduation requirements last semester but did not apply to graduate Fall 2020, except I am in EECS not L&S CS. I want to withdraw from my classes and graduate in SP21 as a not enrolled student. I was wondering if anyone knows the process for CoE, similar to l&s's https://lsadvising.berkeley.edu/progress-planning/preparing-graduation section "Not enrolled in UC Berkeley during EGT term - Extra steps.", where they need to fill out a Google form. Thanks!
history.subject: EECS graduation without enrolling
